ision%20on%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20PIL%20as%20it%20was%20filed%20by%20a%20lawyer%20and%20not%20by%20aggrieved%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20are%20you%20(lawyer)%20coming%3F%20Let%20the%20students%20come%20here%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CJI%20told%20the%20lawyer%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3Bwhile%20declining%20the%20above%20PIL%2C%20we%20express%20nothing%20on%20merits%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20asked%20advocate%20Ujjawal%20Gaur%2C%20who%20has%20filed%20the%20PIL%20as%20a%20petitioner%2C%20to%20focus%20on%20some%20legal%20matters%20and%20leave%20such%20issues%20for%20aggrieved%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20was%20filed%20against%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Union%20education%20ministry%20and%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20to%20cancel%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%20following%20inputs%20that%20its%20integrity%20may%20have%20been%20compromised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20on%20June%2019%20had%20ordered%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%20and%20handed%20over%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20CBI%20for%20an%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20plea%2C%20Mr%20Gaur%20also%20sought%20a%20direction%20to%20immediately%20stay%20the%20proposed%20re-examination%20of%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%20until%20the%20CBI%20completes%20its%20inquiry%20into%20the%20paper%20leak%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20petitioner%20asserts%20that%20the%20decision%20is%20not%20only%20arbitrary%20but%20also%20unjust%2C%20given%20the%20recent%20findings%20of%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CBI's%20investigation%20brings%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20evidence%20suggesting%20the%20paper%20leak%20is%20doctored%2C%20thus%20nullifying%20the%20grounds%20on%20which%20the%20cancellation%20was%20based%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20plea%2C%20filed%20through%20advocate%20Rohit%20Pandey%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20submitted%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bunwarranted%26quot%3B%20cancellation%20of%20the%20exam%20has%20caused%20significant%20distress%2C%20anxiety%2C%20and%20an%20unnecessary%20expenditure%20of%20resources%20for%20the%20aspirants%20who%20have%20rigorously%20prepared%20for%20this%20crucial%20examination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722238860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fnvjq782_supreme-court_625x300_25_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-refuses-to-hear-plea-against-ugc-net-let-students-come-6213129%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20refused%20to%20entertain%20a%20PIL%20challenging%20the%20government's%20decision%20to%20cancel%20the%20UGC-NET%20examination%20following%20alleged%20question%20paper%20leak.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-refuses-to-hear-plea-against-ugc-net-let-students-come-6213129%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Olympics%20Live%3A%20Ramita%20In%20Trouble%20After%2010%20Shots%20During%2010m%20Air%20Rifle%20Final%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOlympics%202024%20Day%203%20Live%20Updates%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Ramita%20Jindal%20is%20in%20action%20in%20the%20women's%2010m%20air%20rifle%20final.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20team%20of%20Manu%20Bhaker%20and%20Sarabjot%20Singh%20along%20with%20Rhythm%20Sangwan%20and%20Arjun%20Singh%20Cheema%20compete%20in%20the%2010m%20air%20pistol%20mixed%20team%20qualification.%20The%20Indian%20men's%20badminton%20doubles%20duo%20of%20Satwiksairaj%20Rankireddy%20and%20Chirag%20Shetty's%20second%20round%20Group%20C%20match%20against%20Germany's%20Marvin%20Seidel%20and%20Mark%20Lamsfuss%20has%20