ing%20to%20Section%20234A%2C%20you%20will%20be%20charged%20interest%20at%20a%20rate%20of%201%20per%20cent%20per%20month%2C%20or%20part%20thereof%2C%20on%20the%20outstanding%20tax%20amount%20from%20the%20due%20date.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20carry%20forward%20of%20loss%20and%20setoff%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFiling%20your%20ITR%20on%20time%20is%20necessary%20if%20you%20have%20incurred%20losses%20from%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20mutual%20funds%2C%20properties%2C%20or%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECarry%20forward%20losses%3A%20Filing%20your%20ITR%20on%20time%20allows%20you%20to%20carry%20forward%20losses%20to%20offset%20them%20against%20future%20income%2C%20which%20reduces%20future%20tax%20liabilities.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENo%20carry%20forward%3A%20Missing%20the%20deadline%20means%20you%20cannot%20carry%20forward%20these%20losses%2C%20which%20may%20lead%20to%20higher%20taxes%20in%20future%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIf%20you%20fail%20to%20file%20Income%20Tax%20Returns%20before%2031%20July%2C%20can%20result%20in%20serious%20consequences%20this%20year%20-%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1)%20No%20Old%20Regime%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndividuals%20who%20have%20opted%20for%20the%20old%20tax%20regime%20and%3Cbr%3E%5Cnhave%20already%20paid%20taxes%20and%20submitted%20investment%20and%20income%20proofs%20according%20to%20this%20regime%2C%20missing%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20CA%20Chirag%20Chauhan%20(%40CAChirag)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCAChirag%2Fstatus%2F1817184067173097670%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2027%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnsure%20you%20file%20your%20ITR%20before%20the%20deadline%20to%20avoid%20these%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722236820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fqcr3aqv_income