%20that%20around%20Rs%202%20crores%20were%20spent%20on%20Manu's%20training%20and%20she%20was%20sent%20to%20Germany%20and%20Switzerland%20for%20it.%20He%20also%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20other%20athletes%20will%20also%20do%20well%20in%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAround%20Rs%202%20crore%20was%20spent%20on%20Manu%20Bhaker's%20training.%20She%20was%20sent%20to%20Germany%20and%20Switzerland%20for%20training.%20Financial%20help%20was%20provided%20which%20was%20needed%20for%20her%20to%20hire%20a%20coach%20who%20she%20wanted.%20We%20are%20providing%20this%20ecosystem%20to%20all%20athletes%20so%20that%20they%20give%20best%20performance%20at%20national%20and%20international%20competitions.%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20our%20athletes%20will%20perform%20well%20in%20Paris%20Olympics%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20shooting%20and%20archery%20competitions%20taking%20place%20today%2C%20Manaviya%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BShooting%20and%20Archery%20competitions%20are%20taking%20place%20today.%20We%20should%20encourage%20our%20athletes%20with%20%23CheerForBharat%20on%20social%20media%20and%20encourage%20them.%20We%20expect%20our%20athletes%20to%20perform%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhaker%20will%20once%20again%20be%20in%20action%20during%20the%2010%20m%20air%20pistol%20mixed%20team%20competition%20qualification%20rounds%20along%20with%20Sarabjot%20Singh%20from%2012%3A45%20PM%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20shooters%20Ramita%20Jindal%20and%20Arjun%20Babuta%2C%20along%20with%20the%20men's%20archery%20team%2C%20will%20aim%20to%20add%20to%20the%20country's%20medal%20count%20at%20the%20ongoing%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Ramita%20made%20it%20to%20the%20final%20of%20the%20women's%2010%20m%20air%20rifle%20event%20after%20a%20fifth-place%20finish%20during%20the%20qualification%20round%2C%20while%20Arjun%20came%20at%20seventh%20in%20the%20men's%20event.%20The%20top%20eight%20players%20from%20both%20the%20qualification%20rounds%20made%20it%20to%20the%20finals%2C%20which%20are%20scheduled%20for%20today%2C%20as%20per%20Olympics.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20men's%20archery%20team%20of%20Dhiraj%20Bommadevara%2C%20Tarundeep%20Rai%20and%20Pravin%20Jadhav%20will%20be%20taking%20on%20Turkiye%20or%20Colombia%20in%20the%20quarterfinals%20at%206%3A31%20PM.%20The%20medal%20rounds%20of%20this%20category%20will%20take%20place%20today%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhaker%20brought%20India's%20first%20medal%20in%20the%20ongoing%20mega%20event%20as%20she%20won%20a%20bronze%20medal%20with%20a%20score%20of%20221.7.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20redemption%20arc%20for%20Manu%20after%20her%20pistol%20malfunctioned%20at%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics.%20She%20made%20history%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20in%2020%20years%20to%20reach%20a%20shooting%20final%20in%20an%20individual%20event%20of%20the%20Olympics%20since%20Suma%20Shirur%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea's%20Ye%20Jin%20clinched%20the%20gold%20medal%20with%20an%20Olympic%20record%20of%20243.2%20points.%20Her%20compatriot%2C%20Kim%20Yeji%2C%20settled%20for%20silver%20with%20241.3%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722236160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F8n263e88_manu-bhaker-x_625x300_29_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fgovernment-spent-rs-2-crore-on-manu-bhakers-training-union-sports-minister-mandaviya-6212644%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mandaviya%20revealed%20that%20around%20Rs%202%20crores%20were%20spent%20on%20Manu's%20training%20and%20she%20was%20sent%20to%20Germany%20and%20Switzerland%20for%20it.%20He%20also%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20other%20athletes%20will%20also%20do%2