-old%20Tanya%20Soni%20liked%20poetry%2C%20was%20a%20regular%20at%20cultural%20events%20in%20college%20and%20determined%20to%20crack%20the%20UPSC%20entrance%20exam%20and%20join%20the%20civil%20services.%20But%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20library%20on%20a%20rainy%20day%20cut%20her%20life%20--%20and%20her%20dreams%20--%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanya%20is%20among%20the%20three%20civil%20service%20aspirants%20who%20died%20after%20rainwater%20flooded%20the%20basement%20of%20Rau's%20IAS%20Study%20Circle%20in%20Delhi's%20Rajendra%20Nagar%20on%20Saturday.%20The%2025-year-old%20was%20originally%20from%20Bihar's%20Aurangabad%2C%20but%20had%20been%20in%20Delhi%20since%20she%20joined%20college.%20After%20completing%20a%20Bachelor's%20degree%20in%20political%20science%2C%20she%20was%20preparing%20for%20the%20IAS%20entrance%20exam.%20Her%20parents%20live%20in%20Telangana%2C%20where%20her%20father%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Vijay%20Kumar%2C%20her%20father%2C%20got%20the%20news%2C%20he%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Lucknow.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20getting%20the%20information%2C%20we%20deboarded%20at%20Nagpur%20and%20took%20a%20flight%20to%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanya's%20body%20is%20on%20its%20way%20to%20her%20Bihar%20home%20for%20the%20last%20rites.%20Vijay%20Kumar%2C%20who%20works%20with%20Singareni%20Collieries%20Company%20Ltd%2C%20said%20becoming%20an%20IAS%20officer%20was%20Tanya's%20childhood%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20her%20Aurangabad%20home%2C%20relatives%20are%20shattered.%20Tanya's%20grandfather%20said%20she%20was%20the%20brightest%20student%20in%20the%20family.%20Her%20cousin%20Ankit%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20very%20sharp%2C%20the%20sharpest%20among%20us%20all.%20She%20loved%20poetry.%20She%20was%20also%20interested%20in%20dancing%20and%20would%20perform%20at%20college%20functions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanya%20was%20among%20the%2020-odd%20students%20in%20the%20library%20in%20the%20coaching%20centre's%20basement%20Saturday%20evening%20when%20a%20downpour%20sent%20water%20gushing%20in%20and%20trapped%20the%20students.%20Three%20students%20died%20and%20the%20others%20were%20rescued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20sparked%20massive%20outrage%20at%20civic%20negligence%20and%20main%20Opposition%20BJP%20has%20targeted%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20which%20is%20in%20power%20in%20Delhi%20and%20also%20controls%20the%20municipal%20corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigation%20into%20the%20tragedy%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20institute%20had%20turned%20the%20basement%20into%20a%20library%20in%20violation%20of%20norms.%20Seven%20people%2C%20including%20the%20owners%20of%20the%20coaching%20centre%20and%20the%20basement%2C%20have%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722235320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fhqe62bgo_tanya-soni_625x300_29_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraus-ias-study-circle-rajinder-nagar-delhi-basement-horror-victim-tanya-soni-loved-poetry-ias-was-her-dream-6212868%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Twenty-five-year-old%20Tanya%20Soni%20liked%20poetry%2C%20was%20a%20regular%20at%20cultural%20events%20in%20college%20and%20determined%20to%20crack%20the%20UPSC%20entrance%20exam%20and%20join%20the%20civil%20services.%20But%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20library%20on%20a%20rainy%20day%20cut%20her%20life%20--%20and%20her%20dreams%20--%20short.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraus-ias-study-circle-rajinder-nagar-delhi-basement-horror-victim-tanya-soni-loved-poetry-ias-was-her-dream-6212868%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraus-ias-study-circle-rajinder-nagar-delhi-basement-horror-victim-tanya-soni-loved-poetry-ias-was-her-dream-6212868%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww