221364%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20still%20from%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20season%20two%20where%20Harry%20Collett%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20multiple%20candles%20in%20a%20dark%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a37e26aab37011780abfc6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221023%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJacaerys%20Targaryen%20(Harry%20Collett)%20originally%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20to%20recruit%20new%20dragonriders%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20season%20two%2C%20episode%20five.%3Cp%3ETheo%20Whiteman%20%2F%20HBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%C4%8Cernjul%20said%20that%20the%20scene%20was%20precisely%20planned%20and%20storyboarded%20months%20in%20advance%2C%20giving%20the%20visual%20effects%20team%20time%20to%20create%20an%20animation%20of%20what%20the%20scene%20would%20look%20like%20for%20the%20directors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20characters%20looked%20like%20the%20actors.%20It%20was%20quite%20amazing.%20It's%20almost%20sad%20that%20nobody%20will%20ever%20see%20those%20amazing%20animations%2C%26quot%3B%20%C4%8Cernjul%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bscary%20part%26quot%3B%20was%20that%20the%20crew%20didn't%20have%20much%20time%20to%20shoot%20such%20a%20crucial%20scene%2C%20%C4%8Cernjul%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dragon%20cave%20scenes%20were%20shot%20over%20two%20days%20on%20a%20bluescreen%20stage%20at%20Warner%20Bros'%20Leavesden%20Studios%20in%20Watford%2C%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20planning%2C%20%C4%8Cernjul%20said%20there%20were%20still%20some%20challenges%20during%20shooting%2C%20because%20the%20scene%20used%20practical%20effects%2C%20including%20fire%2C%20to%20simulate%20the%20dragon's%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20for%20safety%20reasons%2C%20the%20stunt%20people%20could%20only%20be%20on%20fire%20for%20eight%20seconds%2C%20so%20they%20had%20to%20be%20quick%20when%20filming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20you%20are%20aware%20that%20it's%20a%20stunt%20people%2C%20that%20it's%20some%20of%20the%20best%20stunt%20people%20in%20the%20world%2C%20when%20you%20see%20people%20on%20fire%2C%20it's%20really%20unpleasant%20to%20watch%2C%26quot%3B%20%C4%8Cernjul%20said.%20%26quot%3BImagine%2012%20people%20lit%20at%20one%20time%20with%20a%20flame%20thrower.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22922aeea2-74f4-410a-967e-34fe4a21f5e0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPart%20of%20the%20scene%20is%20shot%20from%20Hugh%20Hammer's%20point%20of%20view%20to%20capture%20the%20'danger'%20of%20the%20scene%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221803%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kieran%20Bew%20with%20gray%20hair%20and%20a%20bear%20as%20Hugh%20Hammer%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a37e66a0fc5856d597a656%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221352%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHugh%20Hammer%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20first%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20season%20two.%3Cp%3EHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%C4%8Cernjul%20said%20episode%20seven%20director%2C%20Loni%20Peristere%2C%20had%20a%20request%20early%20on%3A%20To%20do%20an%20entire%20scene%20in%20one%20shot%20from%20a%20character's%20point%20of%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-hugh-hammer-house-of-the-dragon-vermithor-rider-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHugh%20Hammer%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20the%20chosen%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20season%20two%2C%20Hugh%20is%20introduced%20as%20an%20ordinary%20blacksmith%2C%20but%20in%20episode%20seven%2C%20he%20tells%20his%20wife%20that%20he%20is%20the%20child%20of%20a%20Targaryen%20and%20aims%20to%20claim%20a%20dragon%20so%20that%20he%20has%20the%20power%20to%20protect%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHugh%20claims%20his%20mother%20was%20an%20aunt%20of%20King%20Vis