%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20season%20two.%3Cp%3EOllie%20Upton%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Hugh%20claims%20his%20dragon%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-ulf-white-house-of-the-dragon-silverwing-dragonrider-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUlf%20White%3C%2Fa%3E%20becomes%20the%20new%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20episode%20three%2C%20Ulf%20tells%20a%20group%20of%20bar%20patrons%20that%20his%20father%20was%20Baelon%20the%20Brave%2C%20making%20him%20another%20illegitimate%20sibling%20of%20King%20Viserys%20and%20Daemon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUlf%20reluctantly%20goes%20to%20Dragonstone%20to%20claim%20a%20dragon%20and%20somehow%20escapes%20Vermithor's%20savage%20attack.%20However%2C%20as%20he%20stumbles%20through%20the%20cave%2C%20he%20comes%20across%20another%20dragon%2C%20Silverwing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESilverwing%20doesn't%20kill%20Ulf%20and%20instead%20lets%20the%20bastard%20be%20his%20rider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C4%8Cernjul%20said%20scene%20was%20shot%20on%20the%20same%20stage%20as%20the%20previous%20one.%20For%20the%20massacre%20scene%2C%20a%20raised%20platform%20was%20put%20up%20to%20represent%20the%20jetty%20platform%20that%20leads%20into%20the%20dragon%20cave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20removed%20the%20jetty%20and%20lit%20it%20in%20a%20different%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20%C4%8Cernjul%20said%20about%20how%20they%20filmed%20Ulf's%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C4%8Cernjul%20said%20Peristere%20was%20integral%20for%20helping%20the%20actors%20know%20what%20the%20dragon%20was%20doing%20in%20both%20scenes%2C%20because%20they%20only%20had%20a%20small%20puppet%20to%20visualize%20the%20dragon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeristere%20used%20a%20special%20audio%20system%20that%20%C4%8Cernjul%20called%20%26quot%3Bthe%20voice%20of%20god%26quot%3B%20to%20talk%20to%20each%20actor%20directly%20while%20filming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20talking%20to%20them%20in%20real%20time%2C%20and%20then%20he%20