s%2Ftimes-when-shraddha-kapoor-aced-her-looks%2Fphotostory%2F112094711.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112094711.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETimes%20when%20Shraddha%20Kapoor%20aced%20her%20looks%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftimes-when-shraddha-kapoor-aced-her-looks%2Fphotostory%2F112094711.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Month%20Before%20Delhi%20Basement%20Deaths%2C%20IAS%20Aspirant's%20SOS%20Flagged%20Huge%20Risk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20month%20before%20waterlogging%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20a%20building%20in%20Delhi's%20Rajinder%20Nagar%20left%20three%20civil%20service%20aspirants%20dead%2C%20a%20complaint%20had%20flagged%20risks%20in%20using%20the%20basement%20as%20a%20library%20or%20for%20holding%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishor%20Singh%20Kushwah%2C%20a%20civil%20service%20aspirant%2C%20says%20he%20had%20written%20to%20the%20Centre%2C%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20about%20how%20Rau's%20IAS%20Study%20Circle%20was%20using%20the%20basement%20as%20a%20library%20and%20endangering%20the%20lives%20of%20students%20and%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MCD%2C%20it%20has%20emerged%2C%20had%20only%20allowed%20use%20of%20the%20basement%20for%20storage%20and%20parking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%2C%20addressed%20to%20Kumar%20Mahendra%2C%20executive%20engineer%20of%20the%20building%20department%20in%20Karol%20Bagh%20zone%2C%20states%20that%20Rau's%20IAS%20is%20using%20the%20basement%20for%20classes%20without%20a%20No-Objection%20Certificate%20from%20the%20authorities.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20endangering%20the%20lives%20of%20students%20and%20staff%20and%20may%20lead%20to%20a%20big%20accident%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%20Mr%20Kushwah%20also%20alleged%20corruption%20and%20demanded%20strict%20action%20against%20UPSC%20coaching%20centres%20that%20are%20violating%20safety%20norms%20and%20putting%20students'%20lives%20in%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%20sent%20two%20reminders%2C%20urging%20authorities%20to%20take%20action.%20On%20July%2015%2C%20he%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BSir%2C%20it's%20very%20important%20and%20urgent%20issue%2C%20take%20strict%20action%20on%20it.%26quot%3B%20In%20another%20reminder%20dated%20July%2022%2C%20Mr%20Kushwah%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BSir%2C%20please%20take%20action%2C%20it's%20(an)%20issue%20of%20student%20safety.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20online%20portal%20states%20that%20the%20matter%20is%20under%20process.%20Before%20the%20issue%20could%20be%20resolved%2C%20a%20downpour%20on%20Saturday%20evening%20led%20to%20the%20flooding%20of%20the%20basement.%20At%20least%2020%20students%2C%20who%20were%20in%20the%20library%20of%20the%20IAS%20coaching%20centre%2C%20were%20trapped.%20While%20some%20of%20them%20could%20be%20rescued%2C%20Tania%20Soni%20and%20Shreya%20Yadav%2C%20both%2025%2C%20and%20Navin%20Delvin%2C%2028%2C%20died.%20The%20incident%20has%20sparked%20protests%20and%20outrage%20as%20people%20accuse%20civic%20authorities%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20government%20of%20negligence%20that%20cost%20the%20students%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWatch%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20complaint%20was%20filed%20against%20Rau%20Coaching%20Institute%20a%20month%20ago%20regarding%20the%20illegal%20operation%20of%20a%20library%2C%20but%20no%20action%20was%20taken%2C%20If%20action%20had%20been%20taken%20earlier%2C%20this%20incident%20would%20not%20have%20occurred%2C%20%26quot%3B%20says%20Kishore%20(student)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2WYQb8kUEy%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F2WYQb8kUEy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20IANS%20(%40ians_india)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fians_india%2Fstatus%2F1817458597040738539%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2028%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishor%20Singh%20Kushwah%20said%20he%20had%20complained%20against%20Rau's%20IAS%20Study%20Circle%20through%20the%20government's%20public%20grievance%20portal.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20administration%20acted%20in%20time%2C%20this%20tragedy%20could%20have%20been%20avoided%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20basement%20libraries%20in%20Rajinder%20Nagar%20are%20illegal.%20They%20have%20no%20FIR%20safety%20clearance.%20And%20the%20staircases%20are%203%20feet%20-%204%20feet%20wide%2C%20if%20there%20is%20an%20emergency%2C%20so%20many%20students%20cannot%20rush%20out%20easily%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civil%20service%20aspirant%20said%20he%20blames%20the%20administration%20for%20the%20students'%20death.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20had%20taken%20strict%20action%2C%20this%20would%20not%20have%20happened.%20Officials%20of%20the%20administration%20take%20bribes%20and%20give%20clearance%20to%20such%20coaching%20centres%20and%20they%20never%20check%20if%20the%20rules%20are%20being%20followed.%20MCD%20is%20100%20per%20cent%20responsible%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kushwah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20fire%2C%20the%20MCD%20has%20now%20sealed%2013%20coaching%20centres%20in%20Old%20Rajinder%20Nagar%20area%20as%20part%20of%20a%20crackdown%20on%20illegal%20and%20dangerous%20use%20of%20basements.%20These%20include%20IAS%20Gurukul%2C%20Chahal%20Academy%2C%20Plutus%20Academy%2C%20Sai%20Trading%2C%20IAS%20Setu%2C%20Topper's%20Academy%2C%20Dainik%20Samvad%2C%20Civils%20Daily%20IAS%2C%20Career%20Power%2C%2099%20Notes%2C%20Vidya%20Guru%2C%20Guidance%20IAS%2C%20and%20Easy%20for%20IAS.%20%26quot%3BThese%20coaching%20centres%20were%20found%20to%20be%20operating%20in%20basements%20in%20violation%20of%20rules%20and%20they%20were%20sealed%20on%20the%20spot%20and%20notices%20were%20pasted%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%20have%20arrested%20the%20owner%20and%20coordinator%20of%20the%20IAS%20coaching%20centre%20after%20the%20basement%20tragedy.%20They%20face%20charges%20of%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%20and%20causing%20death%20due%20to%20negligence.%20%26quot%3BA%20gross%20criminal%20negligence%20is%20found%20on%20part%20of%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20institute%20in%20ensuring%20safety%20measures%20as%20the%20library%20in%20the%20basement%20was%20running%20illegally%20and%20had%20only%20one%20entry%20and%20exit%20point%20that%20was%20biometric-enabled%20and%20got%20locked%20due%20to%20the%20flooding%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20MCD%20official%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20mayor%20Shelly%20Oberoi%20has%20ordered%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20incident%20to%20find%20out%20if%20any%20MCD%20officer%20is%20involved%20in%20the%20negligence%20that%20led%20to%20the%20tragedy.%20She%20has%20also%20said%20all%20coaching%20centres%20that%20have%20violated%20the%20law%20would%20face%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722227340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fri1qb6q_rau-study-circle_625x300_28_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraus-ias-rajendra-nagar-delhi-basement-deaths-month-before-delhi-basement-deaths-ias-aspirant-posted-sos-sought-action-6211910%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20month%20before%20waterlogging%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20a%20building%20in%20Delhi's%20Rajinder%20Nagar%20left%20three%20civil%20service%20aspirants%20dead%2C%20a%20complaint%20had%20flagged%20risks%20in%20using%20the%20basement%20as%20a%20library%20or%20for%20holding%20classes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraus-ias-rajendra-nagar-delhi-basement-deaths-month-before-delhi-basement-deaths-ias-aspira