pokesperson%20declined%20to%20respond%20to%20Woods'%20allegations%20and%20said%20that%20the%20agency%20%26quot%3Bis%20committed%20to%20better%20understanding%20what%20happened%20before%2C%20during%2C%20and%20after%20the%20assassination%20attempt%20of%20former%20President%20Trump%20to%20ensure%20that%20never%20happens%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWoods'%20team%20included%20countersnipers%20stationed%20at%20the%20American%20Glass%20Research%20building%2C%20which%20was%20used%20as%20a%20staging%20area%20for%20local%20law%20enforcement%20supporting%20the%20Secret%20Service's%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F07%2F28%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-shooting-thomas-crooks-secret-service.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Sunday%20published%20several%20text%20messages%20among%20countersnipers%20there%2C%20which%20showed%20that%20they%20identified%20the%20gunman%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthomas-crooks-academic-transcript-good-grades-chewing-gum-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThomas%20Crooks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20at%20least%20two%20hours%20before%20the%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomeone%20followed%20our%20lead%20and%20snuck%20in%20and%20parked%20by%20our%20cars%2C%20just%20so%20you%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20message%20said.%20The%20countersniper%20then%20reported%20that%20Crooks%20had%20moved%20to%20a%20picnic%20table%20%26quot%3Babout%2050%20yards%20from%20the%20exit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20hour%20later%2C%20a%20countersniper%20took%20photos%20of%20Crooks%20and%20said%20they%20believed%20the%20gunman%20brought%20a%20rangefinder.%20Those%20photos%20later%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20wanna%20notify%20SS%20snipers%20to%20look%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20countersniper%20wrote%20in%20a%20message%2C%20calling%20in%20the%20potential%20threat%20to%20the%20command%20center.%3C%2Fp