0buildings%20full%20of%20vintage%20chandeliers%20and%20whimsical%20decor.%20It%20perfectly%20embodies%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-overlooked-countries-lifelong-traveler-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGeorgian%20capital's%20boho%20but%20brutalist%20vibe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20here%20that%20when%20the%20wind%20rattled%20the%20metal%20roof%20of%20the%20building%2C%20I%20closed%20my%20eyes%2C%20thinking%20of%20the%20waves%20crashing%20on%20the%20beach.%20My%20boyfriend%20Misha%20sat%20upright%2C%20pale%2C%20eyes%20wide%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThat%20sounds%20like%20bombs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMisha%20comes%20from%20the%20small%2C%20mountainous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeen-to-100-countries-my-top-favorite-picks-2024-5%23i-cant-get-enough-of-georgia-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECaucasian%20country%20of%20Georgia%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20located%20at%20the%20crossroads%20of%20Eastern%20Europe%20and%20Western%20Asia.%20He%20is%2037%20and%20has%20lived%20through%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20the%20Georgian%20Civil%20War%2C%20the%20Russo-Georgian%20War%2C%20and%20the%20Rose%20Revolution.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20teenage%20years%20in%20the%201990s%20were%20spent%20back%20in%20the%20US%20and%20were%20dominated%20by%20suburban%20grunge%20ennui%2C%20the%20woes%20of%20dial-up%20modems%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20age%20on%20my%20fake%20ID%20never%20quite%20matched%20my%20baby%20face.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreadlines%2C%20political%20unrest%2C%20violence%2C%20and%20uncertainty%20marked%20Misha's%20formative%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298681cb8-36e1-48b9-9ebe-f85621c76bcf%5C%22%3EThe%20language%20and%20cultural%20chasm%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMisha%20and%20my%20vast%20differences%20encompass%20much%20more%20than%20individual%20interpretations%20of%20what%20the%20sound%20of%20wind%20rushing%20through%20a%20metal%