x%20wrestlers%2C%20five%20of%20whom%20are%20women%20from%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20rural%20landscape%2C%20where%20they%20once%20faced%20stiff%20opposition%20to%20entering%20the%20male-dominated%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMeet%20the%20team%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20wrestling%20contingent%20in%20Paris%20comprises%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20(50kg)%20from%20Charkhi%20Dadri%2C%20Antim%20Panghal%20(53kg)%20from%20Hisar%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263525%2Fanshu-malik-first-indian-woman-world-wrestling-championship-winner%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Anshu%20Malik%20(57kg)%20from%20Jind%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Nisha%20Dahiya%20(68kg)%20from%20Panipat%2C%20Reetika%20Hooda%20(76kg)%20from%20Rohtak%2C%20along%20with%20the%20lone%20male%20wrestler%2C%20Aman%20Sehrawat%20(57kg)%20from%20Jhajjar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COlympics%20is%20every%20sportsperson%E2%80%99s%20dream%2C%20and%20I%20am%20feeling%20happy%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20sporting%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Reetika%20Hooda%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Kharkara%20Village%20in%20Rohtak.%20%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%20leading%20the%20Indian%20charge%20in%20Paris%20is%20a%20great%20motivation%20for%20its%20future%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20Olympics%20at%20the%202004%20Athens%20Games%2C%20and%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%20made%20their%20debut%20at%20the%202012%20London%20Olympics.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20Phogat%20family%20has%20been%20represented%20in%20every%20Olympic%20Games%2C%20including%20in%20Paris%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20started%20with%20Mahavir%E2%80%99s%20eldest%20daughter%20Geeta%2C%20who%20became%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20Olympics%20at%20the%202012%20London%20Games.%20In%20the%20next%20editi