9s%20human-centric%20approach%20is%20also%20driven%20by%20its%20urge%20to%20blend%20nature%20with%20design.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20strive%20to%20create%20experiences%20that%20engage%20and%20nourish%20the%20senses%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20%E2%80%98light%E2%80%99%20as%20a%20building%20material%20and%20respect%20the%20five%20senses%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F340084%2Fgujarat-school-for-the-blind-and-visually-impaired-inclusive-design-architecture-by-anand-sonecha-sealabs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esight%2C%20sound%2C%20smell%2C%20touch%2C%20and%20taste%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20while%20working%20with%20the%20five%20elements%20of%20nature.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClimate%20plays%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20their%20designs%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20tropical%20context%20of%20India.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20towards%20creating%20naturally%20comfortable%20internal%20conditions.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20integrate%20nature%20into%20the%20built%20form%2C%20blurring%20the%20gap%20between%20outdoor%20and%20indoor%2C%E2%80%9D%20Swetha%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Titan%20Integrity%20office%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20a%20prime%20example%20of%20the%20firm%E2%80%99s%20ideology%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20only%20one.%20Karunashraya%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20hospice%20for%20terminally%20ill%20patients%2C%20stands%20out%20as%20a%20significant%20project%20by%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindustan%20Unilever%20Research%20Center%20in%20Bengaluru%20further%20showcases%20Mindspace%20Architects%E2%80%99%20commitment%20to%20harnessing%20natural%20forces.%20Swetha%20shares%20that%20its%20courtyards%20and%20verandahs%20seamlessly%20merge%20the%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20spaces%2C%20allowing%20birds%20to%20fly%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vellore%20International%20School%20in%20Chennai%20is%20another%20example%20of%20their%20principles%20in%20