%5C%22%3EThe%20office%20is%20wrapped%20around%20by%20trees%20with%20a%20bio%20lake%20flowing%20through%20it%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20presented%20two%20distinct%20options%2C%20and%20the%20company%20selected%20the%20second%20option%20based%20on%20its%20response%20to%20the%20biophilic%20design%20brief%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20The%20design%20aimed%20to%20foster%20a%20fulfilling%20connection%20with%20nature%2C%20promoting%20health%2C%20fitness%2C%20and%20overall%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20concept%20of%20creating%20a%20%E2%80%98bio%20lake%E2%80%99%20influenced%20the%20design.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20bio%20lake%2C%20positioned%20on%20the%20eastern%20side%20of%20the%20site%2C%20harmonises%20with%20the%20natural%20and%20organic%20contours%20of%20the%20existing%20lake%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20office%20buildings%20and%20all%20the%20facilities%20are%20placed%20around%20this%20bio%20lake%20to%20emphasise%20the%20panoramic%20views%20and%20immerse%20users%20in%20a%20peaceful%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20office%20is%20located%20on%20a%206.5-acre%20site%20with%20a%20lake%20on%20the%20eastern%20side.%20The%20design%20takes%20full%20advantage%20of%20the%20site%E2%80%99s%20natural%20features.%20The%20building%20is%20oriented%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20its%20longer%20side%20faces%20north-south%2C%20allowing%20glare-free%20natural%20light%20into%20the%20space.%20Porosity%20in%20planning%20and%20form%20allows%20continuous%20movement%20of%20breeze%2C%20ensuring%20natural%20ventilation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwetha%20also%20emphasises%20that%20she%20focused%20on%20merging%20aesthetics%20with%20sustainability.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20three-floor%20structure%20has%20terrace%20gardens%20at%20every%20level%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20cascading%20rice%20fields%2C%E2%80%9D%20Swetha%20notes.%20The%20terraces%20provide%20insulation%20to%20the%20office%20spaces%20below%2C%20reducing%20heat%20and%20aligning%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20sustainable%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBpit4xKHeam%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBpit4xKHeam%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBpit4xKHeam%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Mindspace%20(%40mindspacearchitects)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20terraces%20also%20offer%20outdoor%20working%20spaces%20and%20trails%20for%20leisurely%20walks.%20%E2%80%9CA%20walk%20along%20the%20green%20walk%20path%20covers%20around%20650%20metres%2C%E2%80%9D%20Swetha%20adds.%20%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20greenery%20on%20the%20receding%20terraces%20will%20embrace%20the%20built%20form%2C%20making%20it%20a%20non-building.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20design%20of%20the%20Titan%20Integrity%20office%20reflects%20Titan%E2%80%99s%20core%20values%20of%20design%20edge%2C%20innovation%2C%20ethics%2C%20and%20trust.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20building%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356567%2Fexperiential-homestay-north-collective-in-naggar-shimla-himachal-pradesh-rahul-bhushan-kath-kuni-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98nature%20campus%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20thickly%20wooded%20trees%20and%20water%20bodies.%20The%20combination%20of%20low-rise%20buildings%20surrounded%20by%20landscape%2C%20water%20bodies%2C%20walkways%2C%20and%20outdoor%20meeting%20spaces%20creates%20an%20environment%20akin%20to%20a%20university%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20used%20natural%20materials%20in%20the%20construction%20to%20follow%20their%20idea%20of%20sustainability.%20Swetha%20notes%20that%20they%20used%20cobblestones%20and%20unpolished%20granite%20for%20pathways.%20The%20exterior%20walls%20are%20dry-clad%20in%20granite%20with%20an%20insulating%20air%20gap%2C%20which%20helps%20reduce%20the%20ambient%20temperature%20of%20the%20interiors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Titan%20Integrity%20office%20boasts%20several%20unique%20architectural%20features.%20Swetha%20explains%20that%20the%20office%20has%20a%20central%20spine%20along%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20clear%20water%20body%2C%20which%20is%20a%20double-height%20linear%20space.%20This%20area%20includes%20wide%20steps%2C%20courtyards%2C%20product%20display%20walls%2C%20seating%2C%20and%20informal%20meeting%20spaces%2C%20all%20leading%20to%20an%20atrium%20that%20connects%20to%20the%20dining%20block%20by%20the%20serene%20water%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-42-1721389434.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20office%20remains%20cool%20naturally%20during%20summers%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F